    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/18ce3975a6e8a053218abd3c67437e55.poster.avif?t=1762876551\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/18ce3975a6e8a053218abd3c67437e55.webm?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/18ce3975a6e8a053218abd3c67437e55.mp4?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>吃，射，跃，不停歇</strong> <br>Monkey Splash!!  是一款街机动作平台游戏，以猴子、跳水和世界各地的历史地标为特色！发射果汁光束以助力你的时髦猴子登上这些巨大建筑，以获得最佳高度。请小心，对手跳水运动员、健身狂兔和反抗鸭子将试图结束你的水中有氧之旅！只有最调皮的人才能登上顶峰...<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>射击升空：</strong> 简单的一键控制<br></li><li><strong>水源污染：</strong> 致命的跳水敌人挡住了你的路；这将是一段危险的攀爬。<br></li><li><strong>每日一果：</strong> 各种果味助力道具将为你的旅程增添色彩。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/f008d83c328bad45ef6f8ad295ddf53f.poster.avif?t=1762876551\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/f008d83c328bad45ef6f8ad295ddf53f.webm?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/f008d83c328bad45ef6f8ad295ddf53f.mp4?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>夏日和声：</strong> 每个世界地标都有不同的阳光沐浴俱乐部节拍。<br></li><li><strong>猿猴之趣：</strong> 一群滑稽的猴子将让你笑逐颜开！<br></li><li><strong>完美十分：</strong> 寻找隐藏的明信片，争夺最佳关卡分数！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/91eeb016692cfb052b8b50ed43a9a504.poster.avif?t=1762876551\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/91eeb016692cfb052b8b50ed43a9a504.webm?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/91eeb016692cfb052b8b50ed43a9a504.mp4?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>兔子竞赛：</strong> 快节奏关卡，以强壮的杰罗姆·杰克兔为特色。<br></li><li><strong>躲避鸭子：</strong> 全新的首领关卡，与焰鸭子对决。<br></li><li><strong>世界小知识：</strong> 从顶级旅行者尼德·复活岛头上了解一些事实。 </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/868a0cd9ccfe9b581f673c647a27aebe.poster.avif?t=1762876551\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/868a0cd9ccfe9b581f673c647a27aebe.webm?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353950/extras/868a0cd9ccfe9b581f673c647a27aebe.mp4?t=1762876551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
